com.ontolabs.ayllu.algorithm.bigdata

Interface ParallelLearner

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseParallelLearner, ParallelBoostingClassifier

    public interface ParallelLearner
    The Interface ParallelLearner is generic for parallelizing Supervised Classification/Regression or Unsupervised Clustering, Outlier etc. The responsibility of the learner is to initialize from the properties given and run learning.
